						<div class="postbody">Ok, I got a 99% funcional all-direction (top down) engine working. (99% because I see some missing tiles in the corners if you're going diagonally).<br /><br />No attribute tables yet. No collisions with BG yet. Had to rewrite how neslib handles scrolling, and rewrite the nmi routine.<br /><br />I'm going to have to drop this project and get back to it...I have so many things to work on right now.<br /><br />Edit, I'm using 4 screen mode, btw.</div>

					
