					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you want to detect the end of vblank, you have to poll $2002 in the vblank handler, after all PPU operations are done, waiting for the overflow flag to be *cleared*.<br /><br />All raster effects timed from the start of the frame should be done in the NMI handler, because you want them to happen every frame, even if the game logic lags, otherwise the image will glitch every time the game slows down.</div>

